    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You can reposition yourself after a foe’s missed swing.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Dex 15, Mobility or trick attack class feature.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: Whenever an opponent misses you with a melee attack, you can take a guarded step as a reaction, as long as you remain within that opponent’s threatened area. If you take this step, you can’t take a guarded step during your next turn. If you take an action to move during your next turn, subtract 5 feet from your total movement.</span></p>",
